% docs/references.bib — canonical bibliography for this project.
%
% Every DOI / arXiv id in this file is checked in CI by
% .github/workflows/VerifyReferences.yml (the doiget `verify` action): each
% reference must resolve to real metadata on Crossref / arXiv, so a fabricated
% or mistyped citation fails CI. No PDFs are downloaded. A reference that is real
% but genuinely unresolvable can be excepted by hand in docs/references.allow.
% Add one entry per work you cite — paper, dataset, or software — with a
